<p>Visit <a
href="https://example.org/path?q=1">https://example.org/path?q=1</a> for
details, or write to <a
href="mailto:me@example.com">me@example.com</a>.</p>
<p>A parenthesised reference (<a
href="https://example.org/page">https://example.org/page</a>) keeps its
bounds.</p>
<p>An address such as <a
href="mailto:user@host.co.uk">user@host.co.uk</a> becomes a mail
link.</p>
